From 3fa6390dec751f64bda1f8400f42ab1345491f82 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Akriti Dinesh <adinesh@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Tue, 22 Jul 2025 23:07:13 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:CP:wifi: ath12k: Add MAC logs with level-based
 filtering

Use debug levels (ATH12K_DBG_L0 to L3) to categorize MAC logs based
on their criticality.

Gate all MAC logs using ath12k_debug_mask_level and print them only
when enabled.

Enable critical MAC logs by default using the debug mask setting
ath12k_debug_mask = 0x00000010.

Signed-off-by: Akriti Dinesh <adinesh@qti.qualcomm.com>
